text: Osmany Juantorena Portuondo (born 12 August 1985) is a Cuban volleyball player with Italian citizenship,Volley: Juantorena a Trento fino al 2015. Ora è italiano - sport.repubblica.it a member of Cuba national volleyball team in 2003–2006 and current member of Italy national volleyball team and Italian club Cucine Lube, bronze medalist of the World League 2005. He is a multiple winner of the CEV Champions League and Club World Championship with the Italian club Trentino. ==References== ==Other websites== * FIVB profile Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban volleyball players
